title: Kyler Murray, Jason Witten returns with La Canfora, Prisco, Eisenberg (Football 3/1)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jason La Canfora, Pete Prisco and Jamey Eisenberg to break down the latest from Kyler Murray's weigh-in a the combine as well as the news that Jason Witten is returning to the Cowboys. Then Brinson, JLC, Ryan Wilson and John Breech start to talk more combine and end up hearing about the time Cal Ripken chewed out JLC in the Yankees clubhouse.
